      • Bid

        public Bid(User user,
           Item item,
           java.util.Date date,
           int price)
        Create a bid on an item.

        Create a bid for an item. If an item is supplied in parameter, then this newly created bid is attached to it.

        Parameters:
        user - User that made the bid.
        item - Item on which the bid is related to.
        date - Date of the bid.
        price - Price of the user bid.
